QuestsSorted.NameClass: If Orc then Meats to Orgrimmar

READ ME:
To get Flightmaster position and Entry ID: - Click on menu "Tools" > "Helper Tools" - Select Flightmaster in game. - In "Helper tools" window, click on button "Target Npc info" - You can found Entry ID in first lline (sample, in "EntryTarget.Add(25153); // Shattered Sun Magi : http://www.wowhead.com/npc=25153" the id is 25153) - You can found Position in second line (sample, in "HotSpots.Add(new Vector3(-1858.24f, 5388.41f, -12.4281f));" position X is -1858.24, position Y is 5388.41 and Z is -12.4281)
To take Flightmaster:
- In the step 2 (While), replace "-1831.95f, 5298.3f, -12.42793f" by Flightmaster position. - In the step 2 (While), replace "300" by Flightmaster max distance (if distance is bigger at the value, flightmaster is skipped)).
- In the step 3 (RunCode), replace "-1831.95f, 5298.3f, -12.42793f" by Flightmaster position. - In the step 3 (RunCode), replace "18940" by the flightmaster entry ID. - In the step 3 (RunCode), replace "TaxiButton13" by the taxi button name (destination), to get name of button, use this script: http://wrobot.eu/forums/topic/1689-useful-scripts/?do=findComment&comment=8447 .
